      "back": "탔어요",
      "romanized": "tasseoyo"
    },
    {
      "id": "cpt_got_off",
      "front": "I got off / got out (내리다 — past)",
      "back": "내렸어요",
      "romanized": "naeryeosseoyo"
    },
    {
      "id": "cpt_arrived",
      "front": "I arrived (도착하다 — past)",
      "back": "도착했어요",
      "romanized": "dochakaesseoyo",
      "grammarNote": "도착하다 is a 하다 verb, so the past form is 도착했어요. All 하다 verbs follow this rule: 하다 → 했어요."
    },
    {
